Class FishingGameModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model
      • FishingGameModel

  • public class FishingGameModel
extends Model
    This is a model of the fishing game that holds all objects that should be presented during the game. This model is responsible for movement, collision, and all other dynamic aspects of the fishing game.
